Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who had it all,\NPirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His final words spurred people\Nto take to the seas in droves:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left everything\Nthis world's got to offer {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men set sail for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the world is in the midst\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...Monkey D. Dragon. He's a revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys... What are you so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a power trying to bring down\Nthe World Government directly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Revolutionary Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dragon is the man who leads it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...I shouldn't have said anything about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're my grandson, I decided\Nnot to capture you on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give the Navy that good excuse,\Nso stay here and rest easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be an excuse,\Nso let's tell them that he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came along with these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take your time and talk with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too casual!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more reluctant to say goodbye, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen your grandpa in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?!\NAll you did was hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I still want my grandson\Nto love me, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That selfishness... You can\Nreally tell that they're related.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
