Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that old man was like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised about Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was special to begin\Nwith because of his lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out front talking to Koby and his buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to go?\NThey're your friends, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It does bring back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it was Luffy who saved Koby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami isn't around either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she wanted to hear\Nstories about the marines...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she decided to let them talk alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to the pool with\NKokoro-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to the Galley-La Company's\Nemployee pool that's behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Nami-san's wearing a bathing suit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go bring drinks or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you guys also crossed\Nthat mountain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That mountain? Oh, no,\Nwe didn't cross Reverse Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? But I saw in a newspaper before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that my grandpa's ship\Ncrossed that mystery mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and entered the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that article was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koby! You shouldn't\Ntell him about it so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's okay, since it's Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could it be okay?!\NHe is a pirate, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Don't just talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Let's see... This is top secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but headquarters' battleships can\Nget through the Calm Belt, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's not 100% reliable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a swarm of Sea Kings several\Ntimes larger than battleships there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a terrible time there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\Nat the bottom of the battleships,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they spread these stones\Ncalled Sea Prism Stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Sea Prism Stones release\Nthe same energy as the sea itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so to the fish in the sea, those ships are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea's energy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! So even when those\Nships pass by on the sea's surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sea Kings wouldn't notice them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, they don't have\Nto go through the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of passing through Reverse Mountain,\Nthe entrance to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They can just enter as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy's scientists are pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some good info.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady! Lady! Aren't you gonna swim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be quiet, Chimney!\NChances like this don't come often!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate lady! This is boring! This is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! I'm eavesdropping right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something you want\Nto broadcast out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig into these epoch-making technologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll always find Dr. Vegapunk,\Na Navy scientist. He's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's really incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, Straw Hat,\Ntake Devil Fruits, like the one you ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already clarified how\Ntheir powers get transmitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, another one of his big\Nachievements over the past few years
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is creating new tech that allows\Nan object to eat a Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... There are some\Namazing guys out there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the world is full of incredible people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized what a small world\NI lived in before I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't come out of that\Nbarrel that day, Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...I bet I would still be buttering up\NAlvida and doing chores for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you were on Alvida's ship!\NThat was really funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, the reason\Nyou were on her ship was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Err... Well... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to go fishing and got\Non a pirate ship by mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! What a bungler!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I was such a coward\Nthat I couldn't even run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But because I was on that ship,\NI was able to meet you, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a mistake after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing chores on that ship\Nin order to meet you, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've kinda become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being trained every day, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, your grandpa doesn't\Nknow how to go easy on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Vice Admiral Garp is a wonderful man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He took us in when we had\Nnowhere to go due to an incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We can train in Navy Headquarters right\Nnow all thanks to Vice Admiral Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his grueling training sure is tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough... but I really appreciate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll at least become able to\Nreturn the favor first, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm gonna get promoted\Nhigh enough to boss him around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Cool, split chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?! It's not split!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't get used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kokoro-san looking like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate lady! Let's play volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you really going back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have dinner with us? Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Properly speaking, we're enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't become close, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san, do you know what the\Nsecond half of the Grand Line is called?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,People call the last sea that\Nlies beyond the Red Line
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,by another name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sea where those who will open\Nthe way to the next era gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who comes to conquer this sea\Nwill indeed be the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san! Let's meet again there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I see you, I'll capture you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get stronger and stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and one day... I'll become a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...N...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Ah... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm sorry! I-I got too full of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so embarrassed! I wanna crawl under a rug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I got carried away, since I saw you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fight me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least get to that level.\NIt's obvious you'll need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's an Admiral we're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we meet, we'll be stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,More amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As I am right now, it's such a wild dream
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that just saying it almost makes me faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, how can you\Nhave faith in me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're still a crybaby, huh, Koby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that I was able\Nto see you two again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a lot of work\Nchasing after these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again in the New World for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's go!\N--Ah, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys'd better be prepared!\NWe'll blow you away in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's see who\Nmakes it to the harbor first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy... didn't you just\Ncreate another crazy enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby is a man who makes\Nthings happen. I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good to see that\Nhe seemed to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if he realizes how the world\Nsees what happened in Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, an island directly under\Nthe Government was annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...although I guess the news that they brought\Ndown CP9 probably won't be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it can't be made public,\Nsince CP9 is a secret organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, Enies Lobby caught fire\Ndue to the Buster Call in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet they claimed that Luffy-san\Nand the others did all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With the entire military force\Nof Enies Lobby at our disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With the power of Buster Call,\Nas strong as an entire country's military...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why in the hell can't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...? Why can't we take a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...from a puny little band of pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy should be protecting Justice...\NThere's no way this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just need to become a\Nbig shot and change it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, to think that he picked\Na fight with the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to get just one crewmate back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how stupid is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're worried about Luffy-san, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that!\NI have nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just looking on from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you two doing slacking off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ahhh!\N--He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 1,000 years too early for you to fool\Naround in a place like this, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No meals for either of you for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san! Water-water meat barbecue is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, say "Ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy! Water-water meat barbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sogeking! When'd you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, guys, keep eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! The smoke is hurting my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So how is it, Robin-chan?! You can\Ntell it was marinated well, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! We heard that you woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Franky Family! Come here and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They're having barbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! There are so many of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, add more meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sodom and Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Giants! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Straw Hat! You woke up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Galley-La is here, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing around the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Shameless girl! What're you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pool, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... something smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceberg-san! No! You shouldn't\Nsee this! This woman is a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking a break from building a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Rejecting a party\Nwould make me less of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better have a seat for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Entrant #1, Sogeking! I'll sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:06.79,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was born on the island of snipers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:10.21,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I never miss my mark
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:13.30,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lulu lala lu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.80,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whether it's a mouse's eyeball, lock on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--Please have these!\N--Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:23.39,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Or even your heart, lock on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys! These are ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, help us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:31.07,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The man who hails from the island of snipers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.78,Sogeking ♪,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lululu, lulu lala...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there and listen, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Pheasant...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you could've escaped\Nfrom CP9 alone if you'd wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just stand by... and let them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaguar D. Saul, the Giant who\Nfought for Ohara 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was a close friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take pride in this attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still keep your head high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, I let you escape\Nthe island according to his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm obligated to watch\Nthe rest of your life to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But after 20 years, you seemed\Nto have no tree to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I judged that I could no longer\Nignore a dangerous bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that bounced around as it was chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all things, I thought\Nthat you wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With this whole thing, I was going\Nto settle everything regarding Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of course, I couldn't predict\Nthat CP9 would be defeated at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally found a tree to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether Saul letting you\Nlive was right or wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you show me the answer from here on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I intend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, live strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohara still lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Pheasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Robin! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you eating meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing that stupid\Nstuff again?! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You too! You're wearing a shirt over\Na bathing suit! That looks stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--Are you tryin' to be Franky?!\N--Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the pirates are having a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally found a tree to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right, Saul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Live together with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... I'll try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Do it! Do it, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do it, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You don't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but since I'm on an enemy ship,\NI used a bit of intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop Ace, your second\Ndivision commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shanks Makes a Move!\NThe Linchpin to the Reckless Era"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
